&lt;p&gt;Along with EMEA, the role takes ownership of benefit programs in the United States, Canada, and Latin America — managing renewals, compliance, and employee experience across the Americas region in partnership with regional HR managers and local brokers. The role also provides ad-hoc support to APAC as required.&lt;/p&gt;
