&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with business stakeholders to enable effective, data-driven decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and deliver dashboards and reports using:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oracle Analytics Server (OAS)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tableau&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Microsoft Power BI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SAP BusinessObjects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and optimize ETL/ELT pipelines using Informatica and Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply AI-assisted (vibe coding) techniques to enhance pipeline development and automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and enforce BI standards, best practices, and governance frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage multiple projects simultaneously with strong attention to detail and timelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure data accuracy, scalability, and performance optimization across BI systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide mentorship and technical guidance to junior BI developers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously identify opportunities for process improvements, automation, and innovation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What qualifications will you need to be successful?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8–10 years of hands-on BI/DW experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong ETL design expertise — Informatica and Python (pandas, PySpark, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced PL/SQL — stored procedures, performance tuning, complex transformations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency across OAS, Tableau, Power BI, and SAP BusinessObjects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with vibe coding for pipeline development and automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Functional knowledge of Oracle EBS modules (GL, AP, AR, OM, INV, or similar)&lt;/li&gt;
