&lt;li&gt;Lead internal investigations across ABAC, fraud, harassment, retaliation, conflict of interest, and financial misconduct matters — including fact-finding, evidence preservation, interview strategy, privilege management, and consequence coordination with HR and Legal.&lt;/li&gt;
