&lt;li&gt;Support the sanctions compliance framework across the Verifone Group — including maintenance of the Sanctions Policy, coordination with the AML/CFT function on screening program oversight, escalation of potential sanctions matches, and monitoring of regulatory developments across applicable regimes (OFAC, EU, OFSI, and UN).Advise senior leadership on sensitive escalations, protective measures for reporting p

