&lt;li&gt;Escalate complex or unresolved issues to the appropriate team members while keeping the customer informed throughout.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate records of all customer interactions, case notes, and resolutions in the ticketing system.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pull and review basic reports to identify trends, open cases, or aging requests that need attention.&lt;/li&gt;
