&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #236fa1;&quot;&gt;What&#39;s Exciting About The Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a chance to join Verifone and be a part of the team building the tooling, automation and infrastructure that power secure, high‑volume payment services used globally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll work hands‑on with technologies like Kubernetes, ELK, Prometheus, Python/Go and modern CI/CD frameworks to shape how software is delivered at scale. Your impact will be visible: from improving observability and reliability across our payment platforms to driving an automate‑first culture that removes manual effort and accelerates delivery for engineering teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Because this role sits at the intersection of DevOps, Platform Engineering and SRE principles, you’ll have the opportunity to influence architecture, introduce best practices, and mentor teams across regions. It’s a role for someone who enjoys solving complex problems, building resilient systems, and helping an organisation evolve into a truly modern engineering environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re excited by ownership, technical depth, and the chance to make a meaningful difference in a global payments ecosystem, this role offers the scale, challenge and growth you’re looking for.&lt;/p&gt;
