&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate an ‘automate-first’ mindset, leading initiatives to automate manual maintenance and repeatable tasks and critical business requests in addition to environment deployment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recommend, design and execute optimizations to improve the observability, performance and overall reliability of Verifone’s payment platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain monitoring and logging solutions to ensure visibility into application performance and security&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advocate DevOps culture, mentoring peers within Application Support Teams&lt;/li&gt;
