&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Managing the preparation of U.S. federal and state and local income tax returns with both internal resources and outside tax providers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assisting with analysis and review of inter-company transactions to ensure completeness and accuracy, as well as with the management of global transfer pricing documentation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assisting in the management of income tax audits with both internal and external resources, including preparing and/or reviewing responses to tax notices and information document requests (IDRs) and determining appropriate strategies for settlement and/or resolution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assisting with important company and functional initiatives and projects such as the transfer pricing strategy, M&amp;amp;A transactions, and various restructurings and legal entity rationalizations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&

